<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id62d1dfe1-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa" identifier="/us/usc/t25/s4168"><num value="4168">§ 4168.</num><heading> Public availability of information</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Each recipient shall make any housing plan, policy, or annual report prepared by the recipient available to the general public.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id62d1dfe2-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/104/330/tIV/s408">Pub. L. 104–330, title IV, § 408</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/105/276/tV/s595/e/14/A">Pub. L. 105–276, title V, § 595(e)(14)(A)</ref>, <date date="1998-10-21">Oct. 21, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/2658">112 Stat. 2658</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
